title: WHIRLING F2 ORB / dialogue both shoes

dialogueTree.title: Composure: "There they both are -- two identica..."
dialogueTree.english: There they both are -- two identical shoes, both *copiously* green and *indiscriminately* snake-skin. Reunited on your feet!
dialogueTree.polish: Oto one: dwa identyczne buty, oba *niezwykle* zielone i *bez wątpienia* z wężowej skóry. Znów razem, na twoich stopach!
dialogueTree.belarusian: Вось яны: дзве ідэнтычныя чаравікі, абедзве *надзвычай* зялёныя і *без сумневу* з змеінай скуры. Зноў разам, на тваіх нагах!

links.title: You: "Wait, these do not look like normal..."
links.english: Wait, these do not look like normal cop shoes...
links.polish: Zaraz, one nie wyglądają jak zwykłe gliniarskie buty...
links.belarusian: Пачакайце, яны не выглядаюць як звычайныя паліцэйскія чаравікі...

links.title: Composure: "It's pretty clear a *normal cop* is..."
links.english: It's pretty clear a *normal cop* is not what you are.
links.polish: To raczej oczywiste, że określenie *zwykły gliniarz* do ciebie nie pasuje.
links.belarusian: Гэта, хутчэй за ўсё, відавочна, што вызначэнне *звычайны паліцэйскі* да цябе не падыходзіць.

links.title: Electrochemistry: "You may be what they call a *big di..."
links.english: You may be what they call a *big dick cop*.
links.polish: Możliwe, że jesteś kimś, kogo zwą *gliną z wielkim kutasem*.
links.belarusian: Магчыма, вы той, каго называюць *гліна з вялікім хуям*.

links.title: Composure: "Good. They're balanced. Comfy. Feel..."
links.english: Good. They're balanced. Comfy. Feels like the only good thing about you right now, truth be told.
links.polish: Dobrze. Są dopasowane. Wygodne. Prawdę mówiąc, to w tej chwili chyba jedyny dobry element ciebie.
links.belarusian: Добра. Яны падыходзяць. Зручныя. Шчыра кажучы, на гэты момант гэта, напэўна, адзіны добры элемент цябе.

links.title: Composure: "Go ahead, just as long as you don't..."
links.english: Go ahead, just as long as you don't discard those crocodile babies.
links.polish: Proszę cię bardzo, byleś tylko się nie pozbywał tych dwóch krokodylowych dziecinek.
links.belarusian: Калі ласка, толькі не пазбаўляйся гэтых двух крокадылавых дзетак.
